OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry and bright start
OL,6,Fin the east, otherwise a day of
OL,7,Fsunshine and scattered showers. Some
OL,8,Fof the showers turning heavy and
OL,9,Fpossibly thundery, especially during
OL,10,Fthe middle of the day. Temperatures
OL,11,Fstill a little below average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome late spells of sunshine
OL,14,Faround this evening, before a band of
OL,15,Frain and blustery winds spread in
OL,16,Fovernight. A milder night than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
