OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FOvernight rain clearing to a
OL,6,Fmix of sunny spells and blustery
OL,7,Fshowers on Tuesday. Some of the
OL,8,Fshowers potentially heavy with a risk
OL,9,Fof thunder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FLighter winds on Wednesday but still
OL,13,Fwith plenty of showers. Turning drier
OL,14,Fand brighter on Thursday, with plenty
OL,15,Fof sunshine by Friday. Feeling much
OL,16,Fwarmer with temperatures above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
